Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being called insolent's a compliment, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:00.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kitsui toki hodo warattoke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When things become tough, \Nthat's when you should laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.87,0:01:06.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}atarashii ashita sagashi ni ikitai no nara{\i0}
