Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shutenmaru, the chief of the Atamayama Thieves Brigade,\Nmade his way to Okobore Town...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to take away the food\Nthat Luffy delivered to its people.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jack from the Animal Kingdom Pirates\Nalso appeared on the scene{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and they undertook a punishing battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, appearing suddenly from the sky was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring those brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon?! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things can't get any worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:03:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Everyone is Annihilated!\NKaido's Furious Blast Breath!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kaido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido is a dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:04:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you see right there is Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido can...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...transform himself into a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here with you! So don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:53.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BAKURA TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:05:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come to execute me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:15.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,OKOBORE TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those shitty brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otsuru-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.61,0:06:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okobore Town is around there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, why did Kaido come to Kuri\Nall of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0},\NZoro-{\i1}ya{\i0}, and I were identified by them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all they know!\NThey don't know about the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's all they know"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing, Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You Straw Hats don't have\Nthe right to blame me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sure it was Luffy's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just say, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:07:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like our captain caused you trouble.\NSorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...looking for me and Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Animal Kingdom Pirates led by Kaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...need two key things\Nto maintain their overwhelming forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, the weapons that Kaido is\Ngetting people to manufacture in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second, the backdoor trade of\Nthe artificial Devil Fruits called SMILEs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which Caesar and Doflamingo were creating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We destroyed that at its root\Nwhich was the factory in Punk Hazard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and captured Caesar\Nwho was necessary for SMILE development.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we destroyed the factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:08:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in Dressrosa where\NDoflamingo, Kaido's important trade partner, ruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we also helped Doflamingo, the buyer,\Nget locked up and brought him to ruin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we picked a fight with Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the only ones he's coming after are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...me and Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't chase! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If more of us get exposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll find out that all the members of\Nthe Straw Hats and the Heart Pirates are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll start a big hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So think rationally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're only seen us so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your plan is still safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what are you two going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could let things be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0} has already gotten involved\Nwith the people of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he lets his emotions take the lead,\Nit'll spell trouble for the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.69,0:09:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all of us aren't there on the execution day,\Nthe alliance is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show yourselves at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Luffy...\NWhat did he do while we were apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat to the forest,\NAtamayama Thieves Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna get involved with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept hearing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there is a mighty thief\Nliving deep in the mountains of Kuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shutenmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...remember you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's forget about the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:12:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you bend your knee to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wipe the slate clean between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Smells like alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido-{\i1}san{\i0}, don't tell me you're drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! I'm not drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's drunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.35,0:13:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do, Shutenmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get away! Let's just fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jack-{\i1}sama{\i0}! I'm trying to stop the bleeding\Nso don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so drunk.\NHe could lose his temper at any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better leave here soon, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the residents of Okobore Town\Nare a valuable work force in the factories!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice just setting an example,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if he wreaks havoc senselessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll all get wiped out along with Kuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to go to Okobore Town, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you cannot, Kiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get identified, too,\Nthe plan will be all screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the fact is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.21,0:14:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}sama{\i0}, I did not tell you\Nbut that's where...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Otsuru-{\i1}san{\i0} lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.09,0:14:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me that sooner, Kiku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, Kin-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go back?!\NI will save Tsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am responsible, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe she did not get remarried to\Nsomeone who would protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has already been 20 years\Nsince I left her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am on my way, Tsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's still so far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy!\NYou think the people of Okobore Town are okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You see?\NWhen a pirate does a good thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido is coming after us, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supreme Commander Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...one of the Headliners?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supreme Commander! If you're looking for\NStraw Hat Luffy and Trafalgar Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:16:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're hiding in the ruins of Oden Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hawkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Straw Hat and Law\Nare hiding in the ruins of Oden Castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I lied to him\Nin order to stop him from rampaging...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These days,\Nmaybe because of that particular legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some people are saying that they've seen\Nsuspicious lights at the top of the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the one that says the Kozuki samurai\Nwho we exterminated will come back for revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, instead of letting it incite\NShogun Orochi's terror,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can kill two birds with one stone\Nby wiping out that abandoned castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we trying to fight him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid for my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My soul left the body before I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop laughing! Don't surprise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Captain's doing alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden Castle, you said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brings back memories...\NIt is indeed a good place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:18:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's where they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took SMILE away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:06.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,LAW AND STRAW HAT'S PIRATE ALLIANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those hateful punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's heading towards the \Nruins of Oden Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Isn't he coming towards us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's noticed that we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to see us from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he heading that way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.89,0:20:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.48,0:20:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We're in trouble, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}...\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.13,0:21:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:23:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:06.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oden Castle has been wiped out in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:08.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It is unknown whether \Neveryone is dead or alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After learning even Otama has been attacked,\NLuffy reaches the breaking point{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and makes a mad dash for Kaido!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.17,0:23:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the memories of his friends in mind,\NLuffy's all-out attack blasts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.93,0:23:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A blistering battle in which\Nneither side gives an inch starts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Finally Clashing! The Ferocious Luffy vs. Kaido!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
